<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Access Denied - SkillSwap</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-500: #6366f1;
      --primary-600: #4f46e5;
      --gray-50: #f9fafb;
      --gray-100: #f3f4f6;
      --gray-400: #9ca3af;
      --gray-500: #6b7280;
      --gray-600: #4b5563;
      --gray-900: #111827;
      --warning-50: #fffbeb;
      --warning-100: #fef3c7;
      --warning-500: #f59e0b;
      --warning-600: #d97706;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning-50) 0%, var(--gray-50) 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .error-container {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    
    .error-illustration {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .lock-icon {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .lock-body {
      width: 80px;
      height: 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning-500) 0%, var(--warning-600) 100%);
      border-radius: 8px;
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 20px;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .keyhole {
      width: 16px;
      height: 24px;
      background: var(--gray-900);
      border-radius: 50% 50% 4px 4px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .keyhole::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -8px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 6px;
      height: 12px;
      background: var(--gray-900);
      border-radius: 0 0 2px 2px;
    }
    
    .lock-shackle {
      width: 50px;
      height: 40px;
      border: 8px solid var(--gray-500);
      border-bottom: none;
      border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0;
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 20px;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
    
    .shield {
      position: absolute;
      right: 10px;
      top: 30px;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
    }
    
    .error-code {
      font-size: 6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--warning-500);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--warning-100);
    }
    
    .error-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .error-message {
      color: var(--gray-600);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .access-reasons {
      background: var(--warning-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--warning-100);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .access-reasons h3 {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--warning-600);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .access-reasons ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .access-reasons li {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--gray-600);
      padding: 0.375rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .access-reasons li::before {
      content: '‚Ä¢';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--warning-500);
    }
    
    .error-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary-500);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-600);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: var(--gray-600);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border-color: var(--gray-400);
    }
    
    .support-info {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    }
    
    .support-info p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
    }
    
    .support-info a {
      color: var(--primary-500);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .support-info a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-illustration">
      <div class="lock-icon">
        <div class="lock-shackle"></div>
        <div class="lock-body">
          <div class="keyhole"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="shield">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="error-code">403</div>
    <h1 class="error-title">Access Denied</h1>
    <p class="error-message">
      You don't have permission to access this page. This area is restricted to authorized users only.
    </p>
    
    <div class="access-reasons">
      <h3>
        <span>üí°</span>
        This might be because:
      </h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You need to log in to view this content</li>
        <li>Your account doesn't have the required permissions</li>
        <li>This page is only for tutors or administrators</li>
        <li>Your session may have expired</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="error-actions">
      <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">
        <span>üîë</span>
        Log In
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
        <span>üè†</span>
        Go Home
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">
        <span>üìß</span>
        Contact Support
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="support-info">
      <p>
        If you believe you should have access to this page, please 
        <a href="/contact">contact support</a> for assistance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
